Package: devPTIpack
Title: Project Targeting Index: a framework for improving portfolio targeting with geospatial dashboards
Version: 0.0.0.9981
Authors@R: c(
  person('Eduard', 'Bukin', email = 'ebukin@gmail.com', role = c('aut')),
  person('Koichi', 'Ito', email = 'koichi19960406@gmail.com', role = c('cre')),
  person('Takaaki', 'Masaki', email = 'tmasaki@worldbank.org', role = c('ctb')),
  person('Arden', 'Finn', email = 'afinn1@worldbank.org', role = c('rev')))
Description: A generic framework for computing and visualising Project Targeting Index
  (PTI) scores -- composite indices derived from weighted socioeconomic indicators
  mapped across hierarchical administrative boundaries in the context of development
  project portfolio management. The package provides a set of tools for computing
  PTI scores, visualising them on interactive geospatial dashboards using R and Shiny.
